    Key Insights: ${researchDossier.researchSummary}

    ROLE & STYLE:
    Role: ${protocol.role}
    Format: ${protocol.style}

    CORE REQUIREMENTS:
    1. **Integration of Scholarship**: You must cite the works provided in the Librarian's Dossier. Do not make up sources.
